What does it mean that nearly half of the global photovoltaic installed capacity is in China?

dataSource.companyValue: What does it mean that nearly half of the global photovoltaic installed capacity is in China?

data.text: Now, nearly half of the world's installed photovoltaic capacity is located in China, more than half of the world's new energy vehicles are driven in China, and a quarter of the world's new green area comes from China. We strive to achieve carbon peak before 2030 and carbon neutrality before 2060. We will do what we say.
